   variation; Insect; Pollination; Population size Seed set; Species
   richness; For plant species ven der Meijden (1990)},
Keywords-Plus = {POPULATION-SIZE; SEED-SET; POLLINATOR BEHAVIOR; PLANT-DENSITY;
